Package: covidscreen
Title: Simulate Asymptomatic Screening for COVID-19
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Jesse', 'Smith', email = 'Jesse.Smith@stjude.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: The {covidscreen} package provides simple simulations for understanding the effects of assurance testing/screening on a population. It aims to help decision-makers determine whether and how to test for COVID-19 with limited resources.
